enchantment.so_many_enchants.health_boos: For each level of health boost will give the wearer one more heart. This stacks with other armor pieces.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.flight.desc: When boots with flight are worn, you will be able to fly. While flying you will lose hunger.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.attack_reac: Weapons with this enchant will have 1.5 more blocks of reach per level.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.block_reach: Tools with this enchant gain one block of reach for breaking blocks per level.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.freezing_at: When you hit enemies they will not be able to move, will dig slower, and will not jump.
When you mine a crop with this enchantment it will automatically be replaced.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.temper.desc: For each level of this enchantment, armor will gain 1 armor toughness.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.reinforceme: For each level of this enchantment, armor will gain 1 armor bar.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.critical.de: For each level of critical, you have 20% more of a chance to do a critical hit without jumping or do more damage with a normal critical
enchantment.so_many_enchants.heavy.desc: For each level of this enchantment, armor will gain 1 knockback resistance.
When worn you will have infinite night vision.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.double_brea: For each level, you have a 20% more of a chancce to break 2 blocks instead of one.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.step_assist: For each level gain 0.5 blocks of step height.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.fast_hopper: Will make a hopper transfer 4 times faster.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.cavernous_s: Adds an extra row to chests and shulker boxes.
Makes furnaces, blast furnaces, and smokers smelt faster.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.fuel_effici: Makes furnaces, blast furnaces, and smokers smelt use fuel less quickly. (It will last longer)
enchantment.so_many_enchants.extra_exper: Makes furnaces, blast furnaces, and smokers smelt give more experience when you take items out.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.heavy_blade: Weapons do a lot more attack damage but attack speed is reduced.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.light_blade: Weapons are a lot faster but do less damage.
enchantment.so_many_enchants.blindness_e: An enchantment that when applied to armor will give the player the Blindness effect at the level of the enchantment. Does not stack.
